  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba\u0d9a \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel queue collision kills tipper truck",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Aluthgama Police said that a man who was queuing for diesel for a lorry at the IOC petrol station in Dharga Town last night (28) had collided with a tipper heading towards Welipenna from Aluthgama while crossing the road in front of the petrol station.",
        "The suspect driver who had caused the accident had gone to Aluthgama town for dinner from the fuel queue in Dharga Town and was returning to Dharga Town when he had crossed the road in front of the fuel depot in Dharga Town at around 11.20 pm and died on the spot, Aluthgama Police said.",
        "The deceased has been identified as Singappulige Ananda (58), a resident of 187/3, Alawatugoda, Puwakwatta, Dharganagara.",
        "The victim was waiting in line at a petrol station with a lorry belonging to another person that night when he was crossing the road in front of the petrol station in Dharga Town on the Welipenna Southern Expressway in Aluthgama.",
        "The body of the deceased has been placed at the Aluthgama Hospital and will be taken to the Nagoda Hospital in Kalutara for postmortem examination.",
        "The suspect tipper driver who caused the accident has been arrested by the Aluthgama Police and is due to be produced before the Kalutara Magistrate's Court today (29)."
      ],
